auth_expired.description:
Authentication for Google Find My Device is invalid or has expired for this entry.

**Entry:** {entry_title}
**Account:** {email}

Select **Reconfigure** on the integration card to sign in again. If you recently changed your Google password or revoked tokens, you must re-authenticate here to restore functionality.

duplicate_account_entries.description:
This Google account (**{email}**) is already configured by another entry:

{entries}

Disable or remove the duplicate entry so that only one entry per account remains active, then reload the integration (or restart Home Assistant).
